# Build artifacts — built fresh inside Docker
dist
**/dist
build
**/build
.next
**/.next
.turbo
**/.turbo

# Logs
*.log
**/logs

# Test artifacts
coverage
**/coverage

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode
.idea
